==事件==
2015年底日本國寶或古蹟陸續傳出遭人潑灑類似油液的事件，至少有6府縣的24家寺院、神社的古蹟遭殃。京都和奈良為重災區，多個國寶級世界文化遺產，包括[[東大寺|東大寺]]及二條城等旅遊熱點，都不能幸免。警方不排除是同一人犯案或有模仿犯，但因神社及寺院範圍廣兼保安鬆散，難以揪出噴油狂徒。<ref>{{cite news | title = 日世遺古寺 屢遭潑油液 | publisher = 世界日報 | url = http://udn.com/news/story/6812/831104-日世遺古寺-屢遭潑油液 | date = 2015-04-12 | accessdate = 2015-04-12 | language = zh-hant | archive-date = 2015-04-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150413020034/http://udn.com/news/story/6812/831104-%E6%97%A5%E4%B8%96%E9%81%BA%E5%8F%A4%E5%AF%BA-%E5%B1%A2%E9%81%AD%E6%BD%91%E6%B2%B9%E6%B6%B2 | dead-url = no }}</ref>

2017年4月三名台灣籍女子進入二之丸御殿，以除靈為名在多處潑撒香灰，時隔一年後在2018年4月破案。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%9F%E8%87%89-%E4%BA%AC%E9%83%BD-%E4%BA%8C%E6%A2%9D%E5%9F%8E-%E8%A2%AB%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%8E%E7%B2%89%E6%9C%AB%E6%B1%99%E6%90%8D-3%E5%8F%B0%E5%A5%B3%E9%81%AD%E9%80%AE-085031620.html|title=丟臉！京都「二條城」被不明粉末汙損 3台女遭逮|accessdate=2018-04-19|language=zh-TW|archive-date=2020-11-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201110171155/https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%9F%E8%87%89-%E4%BA%AC%E9%83%BD-%E4%BA%8C%E6%A2%9D%E5%9F%8E-%E8%A2%AB%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%8E%E7%B2%89%E6%9C%AB%E6%B1%99%E6%90%8D-3%E5%8F%B0%E5%A5%B3%E9%81%AD%E9%80%AE-085031620.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180420/1338415|title=長相曝光！遊日遭逮3台女。還曾到三十三間堂撒粉|accessdate=2018-04-20|language=zh-TW|archive-date=2018-07-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180722083659/https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180420/1338415|dead-url=no}}</ref>

